
Timetabler

Simple constraint-satistfaction problem solver, with a specialized implementation for solving timetable problems.

timetabler.rb         - Executable script to solve a sample problem.
Timetabler/
  CSProblem.rb        - Defines the base CSProblem class, which represents a
                        constraint-satisfaction problem and implements a basic
                        backtracking algorithm to solve it.
  TimetableProblem.rb - A specialized form of CSP.
